Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey tech enthusiasts today,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we're diving into a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,game changer in app
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,development, chat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GPT apps, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,rise of AI -driven
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,interactions, understanding how to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,effectively build these
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,apps is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these apps are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,not just tools, they
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,enhance collaboration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,between users and AI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,models.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Re -shaping how we
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,interact with technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,let's explore how building
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,chat GPT apps is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,fundamentally different from traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditional UI workflows can
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,struggle when you toss
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,an AI model into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,now you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,third entity influencing how
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,information flows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This dynamic requires a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,fresh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,approach to user interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the biggest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,challenges developers face is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,managing the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,information flow between the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,user, the UI, and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditional methods, like just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in -time data fetching,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,often fall flat in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,an agentic environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpic has tackled this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,head -on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by creating an open
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,source framework called Skybridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This framework is a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lifeline for developers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,simplifying the app creation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,process.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the codex skill developed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by Alpic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's designed to help
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,developers ideate, build, test,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and ship their apps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,more efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine having a toolkit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that streamlines your workflow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and enhances productivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This approach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,not only saves time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but also allows for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a more creative development
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,process, tapping into the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,unique characteristics of AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Driven interactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,key takeaways from Alpic's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,journey in building chat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,GPT apps?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we need to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,embrace the AI first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,experience and rethink
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,our traditional app designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, the development process
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is evolving, adapting to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,new challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, whether you're a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,developer or just a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,tech enthusiast, these lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,invaluable for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of app development.
